00:39:55.840 --> 00:39:59.280
<i>Aku suka sedikit lebih agresif.</i>

00:39:59.360 --> 00:40:00.760
<i>Menerobos gawang.</i>

00:40:00.840 --> 00:40:01.880
<i>Haaland!</i>

00:40:03.480 --> 00:40:06.440
<i>Kami mengubah temponya,
kau bisa dapat banyak peluang,</i>

00:40:06.520 --> 00:40:08.240
<i>lalu kau bisa mencetak gol.</i>

